<title>lyt slạmk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- lyt slạmk yạ̉srny lyth ytgẖlgẖl fy
 fạ̉ry ḥbk yḥṣrny wydạk tḥnw ʿly
 flạ ạ̉frạḥ wlạ ạ̉trạḥ wlạ ạ̹nsạn wlạ sẖyṭạn
 wlạ qwạt wlạ ryạsạt tnzʿ ḥbk yạrạʿy
 2- ḥbk ymlạ̉ qlby slạm yrfʿ nfsy mn ạlḍʿf
 yfrgẖ qlby mn ạlạ̉whạm yṭrḥ llkẖạrj kẖwfy
 flạ ạḥtyạj wlạ ạnzʿạj wlạ mạḍy wlạ ậty
 wlạ ạ̉mwạl wlạ ạ̉hwạl tnzʿ ḥbk yạ rạʿy</lyrics>
</song>